{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "第十二回 意外风波\n\n本章主要讲述小鱼儿与白衣少年（后揭示为铁心男）的战斗与对话。小鱼儿利用智慧和点血截脉的技巧，迫使铁心男拜他为师。随后桃花带来消息，称有强盗袭击她的族人，要找一个姓铁的人。铁心男承认自己就是要找的人，决定前往救援。途中遇到李家兄弟和峨嵋山三毛兄弟（毛毛虫、毛公鸡、毛猩猩），展开一场惊险的对峙。\n\n关键情节：\n1. 小鱼儿与铁心男的战斗，展示疯狂一百零八打和点血截脉\n2. 小鱼儿用诡计迫使铁心男拜师\n3. 桃花带来强盗袭击的消息\n4. 铁心男承认身份并前往救援\n5. 遭遇李家兄弟和三毛兄弟\n\n主要人物：\n- 小鱼儿：机智勇敢，善于用计\n- 铁心男：武功高强，但惧怕女人\n- 桃花：草原女子，担心族人安危\n- 三毛兄弟：峨嵋山来的怪人，武功奇特\n\n武功展示：\n- 疯狂一百零八打：铁心男的武功\n- 点血截脉：小鱼儿的技巧\n- 七步阴风掌：小鱼儿虚构的武功",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "‘疯狂一百零八打’，哈哈，果然是疯子才会使的拳法，只可惜这么漂亮的人，却学这种疯子的拳法，真叫人看着难受。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看起来虽难受，用出来更叫别人难受。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我可不难受，我也不要学……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "学",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "疯狂一百零八打",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住手，你这拳法果然不错，我愿意学了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怪不得别人常说，好好的人绝不能和疯子打架，因为他绝对打不过疯子的，如今我才知道这话果然不错",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如今你可知道厉害了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜你不是疯子，否则你使出这套拳法，一定更加厉害……怕只怕你将这套拳法用久了，也会变得有些疯味了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既要拜我为师，怎地如此无礼？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只说要学这套拳法，可没说要拜你为师，师父一样也可以向徒弟学拳的，你说是不是？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还想打么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不能打了，不能打了，你只要再一出手，立刻就要七窍流血而死，我好心告诉你，你可莫要不信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这小鬼满嘴鬼话，也想来骇我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "骇你？我可不是骇你，你可知道武林中有种绝传的秘技，叫‘七步阴风掌’。这就是说，无论是谁，只要在七步外被这种掌风击中，除非他站着不动，否则他走不出七步，嘿嘿，就要送终。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鬼话，世上哪有这种掌法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鬼话",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种掌法绝传已有百年，你自然不知道，但我却在无意中得到绝世奇缘，学会了这种掌法，而……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "而且还打了我一掌，是么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "七步阴风掌",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这次你说对了，不过，我只打了一掌，轻轻的一掌，只要你拜我为师，我还可将你救活。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若以为几句话就可将我吓倒，你就大错而特错了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不信？好，你且摸摸你左面第三根肋骨下是不是有些发疼？这就是中了‘七步阴风掌’的征象。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼哼哈哈",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么样，疼吧？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然疼的，任何人这地方都是最容易觉得疼的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但这不是普通的疼，是特别的疼，就好像被针刺，被火烧一样，疼得热辣辣的．疼得叫人咧嘴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你再摸，不是这里，再往左一点……再往下一点……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对了，就是这里，用力往下按！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "噗",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "饶你精似鬼，也要喝我的洗脚水，如今你终于上了我的当了吧，你可知道是怎么上的当？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "告诉你，世上根本没有‘七步阴风掌’，我自然也不会，但世上却真有另一门神秘的武功，叫做‘点血截脉’。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这‘点血’与‘点穴’虽是一字之差，而且音也近似，但手法却大不相同，点穴是死的，点血却是活的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "期门",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是点穴，你‘期门’与‘气血囊’两处穴道，永远都在这个部位，绝不会动，所以点穴是死的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "点血却是要截断你的血脉，你的血脉不能流通，身子自然不能动，自然要倒下去，你的血脉整天都在不停地流动着，点血就是要恰巧点在你血脉流动时前面那一点，才能恰巧将你的血脉截断。血在流动，这一点自然也时时刻刻都不同，所以点血是活的，你懂得我的意思了么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "懂了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但这闭血点穴为时不能太久，否则被点的人就要死了，方才我已解开你闭住的血，所以你现在才能说话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方才你瞧着地下的影子，可是在计算时辰，计算我血脉该流在何处，然后再叫我用力按下去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对了，举一反三，孺子可教也。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你虽然会一点‘点血’的皮毛，但会的却不多，而且根本就点不着我，所以，你就骗我，让我自己动手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对极对极，一点也不错，因为教我‘点血’的那人，医道虽高明已极，武功却不行已极，他虽对人体各部都了如指掌，虽能算得出人体血脉流动的系统，却也不知道该用什么手法去点，所以我也只有请你代劳了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你还在随时准备动手，所以真气仍在掌指间流动，我一叫你用力，你真气就不觉自指间透出，这自也因为我叫你点的不是穴道，甚至根本不在穴道附近，所以，你就根本未去留意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "诡计伤人，又算得什么！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "诡计？你可知道要多大的学问才能使得出这样的诡计？第一，我要先让你时时刻刻都防备着我，这样你的真气才不会自指掌间撤出；第二，我要先编成‘七步阴风掌’这样一个怕人的名字，让你不得不含糊。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两样已够了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不够，我至少还得略窥‘点血’术的门径，还要算准血脉恰巧正流动在你穴道附近，让你全不提防。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这简直是武功与智慧的结晶，我武功若不高，怎能叫你提防？我智慧若不高，又怎能教你不提防？你先提防而后不提防，可见你这两样都不如我，你拜我这样的人为师，总算不冤吧？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拜你为师，你……你做梦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你未动手前明明已说好的，如今怎能反悔。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你杀了我吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我何必杀你，你若要食言反悔，我就切下你的鼻子，挖去你的眼睛，割下你的舌头，把你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我死都不怕，还怕这些？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真的不怕？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！你既不怕，我就换个法子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我什么都不怕！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我把你吊在树上，脱下你的裤子打屁股，你怕不怕？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你终于还是怕了吧，快叫师父。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你这恶魔……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不叫我师父反叫我恶魔……好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师父！师父……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师父",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你哭什么，有我这样个师父也不错呀。何况，你既已叫了我师父，哭也没有用了……呀，你还哭，再哭我又要打屁股了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这样才乖，对了，你得先告诉我，叫什么名字？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁……铁心男！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兰花的兰？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然是男儿的男。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁心的男儿，好，好名字，男儿的心，本该像铁一样硬，不想你模样虽生得有些像女孩子，名字却取得似乎刚强。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我很想吃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小鱼儿",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想吃，就吃吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不是想吃我的肉么？……告诉你，无论你心里在想什么，都瞒不过我的，我一猜就能猜出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你今年几岁了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "总比你大两岁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小鱼儿！江小鱼！你莫要走！不能走！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阿拉，真主，感谢你……他还在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阿拉？是什么事将你又‘拉’来了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "求求你，莫要再笑我，你打我骂我都可以，但你……你……一定要跟我走！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唉，又多个泪人儿，真要命！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要是再哭，哭肿了眼睛，就不该叫桃花，要叫桃子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "又哭又笑，猫儿撒尿……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗤",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事，新衣服被人弄上鼻涕了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗤",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你嗓子再哭哑些，就学得更像了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我本想冲过去，但想了想，又下了马，伏下身子，在草丛里爬了过去，幸好草很高，我爬到近前，便瞧见那一团帐篷四周，不知何时已被一群人围上了，这些人一个个拿着大刀，又拿着鞭子，凶眉横眼，骑在马上，不像强盗才怪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哎呀，强盗来了，有意思。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些强盗将我的族人和那些做生意的汉客全都赶牛赶羊般赶成一团，我瞧见他们的鞭子抽在我的族人身上，我的心都碎了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "草原上的强盗原来这么凶。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "草原上的强盗虽是汉人，但为了方便，也都是穿着牧人的衣服，但这些强盗的打扮，我一看就知道是从关内来的。他们骑的也不是咱们的藏马，而是川马。藏马的腿长，川马的腿短，我一瞧就能分出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些人不远千里自关内赶来，自然不是为着要抢你们的货物牛羊，关内的有钱人，总比关外多……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "草原上虽有强盗，但却不是这些人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么知不是？草原上的强盗你认得？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们不是要抢东西，而是要抢人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "抢人？抢谁？抢你？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "汉家的女孩子，也总比我们漂亮得多……他们要抢的，也是个汉客，他们一路自关内将他追到这里，而且他们的探子还瞧见这人在我们的帐篷里，所以，他们就逼着我的族人要人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的族人可给了他们？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的族人根本不知道他们要的是谁，他们自己在帐篷里找，也没有找着，于是他们就一定说是我的族人藏起了他，还要限半个时辰内将他交出来，否则……否则他们就要凌辱我们的姐妹，打死我们的兄弟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我来求你回去救救他们，我知道你很有本事……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我本来还以为他们要的人是你，后来才听见，他们要的，是一个‘姓铁的小子’，你……你可知道他是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姓铁的……我没听见过，我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就姓铁，我就是他们要的人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "呆子，你为何要承认？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那些强盗中可有女子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没……没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，他们既要找我，我跟你去！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你去？不行！不行！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只有我去，才能救你的族人，为何不行？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "像你这样的人，去了岂非等于羊入虎口，我怎忍着你前去送死，你……你……你还是快逃吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你以为我怕他们？……哼！像他们这种蠢才，一百个加在一起，也抵不过我一根手指头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不怕他们，为何要从关内逃到这里来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非你怕的只是个女人，是以一听他们全是男的，你就不怕了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些事不用你管。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来你不怕男人，只怕女人，哈哈，这毛病倒和我差不多，我委实也是一见了女人就头疼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放过我……我去！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若去死，我岂非连徒弟也没了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我担保一定回来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "桃花，你看我这徒弟是不是英雄？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阿拉保佑你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "英雄救美人，这可是佳话一段，我江小鱼可不能杀风景……好，你去吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你有了一个英雄还不够么？我……我在这里等你们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不愿救人的人，将来也没有人救你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁……你也上马来呀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多情的姑娘，情总是不专的，这话可一点儿也不错。铁心男这下子被她缠住了，却不知要几时才能脱身。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "马儿马儿，咱们也去瞧瞧热闹好么，但你瞧见漂亮的小母马时，可要走远点，咱们年纪还小，若被女人缠着，可就一辈子不能翻身了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你坐的稳么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若是坐不稳，最好抱住我，免得跌下马去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要你救了我的族人，我……我什么事都答应你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "桃花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们是不是就这样冲进去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁心男在这里！谁要来找我？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，姓铁的，算你还有种，总算没叫我李家兄弟白等。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我早已猜中你们……你们要找的是我，还呆在那里作什么，随我来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好了，你们干什么找我，说吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "独眼大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我兄弟先得问问你，那东西可是在你身上？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，是在我身上，但就凭你们兄弟这几块料，可还不配动它，你们若认为我到关外是躲你们，你们就错了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "独眼大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放屁！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "独眼大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "下来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "李家兄弟的马上刀鞭功夫，原来也不过如此，别人想动我怀里的东西，还有话说，不料你们竟也不掂掂自己的斤两，也想插一脚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "李家兄弟不配动你怀里东西，毛家兄弟配不配？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "峨嵋山上三根毛……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人鬼见了都难逃……嘻嘻，这句话原来你也听过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孩子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "‘嚼心蛀肺’毛毛虫这名字你总听说过吧，那就是我，你最好莫要多瞧，多瞧两眼，就会肚子疼的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 511,
      "line_end": 511
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "毛毛虫",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 515,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你就是毛公鸡？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 517,
      "line_end": 517
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你莫要咬着牙，无论谁见着我，牙齿也要发痒的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 519,
      "line_end": 519
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "毛公鸡",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 527,
      "line_end": 527
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "毛公鸡",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 529,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "猩猩",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 531
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_nan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "毛猩猩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 533,
      "line_end": 533
    }
